alarmitronbackend.UserAlarms

Class UserAlarms

  • java.lang.Object
    • alarmitronbackend.UserAlarms.UserAlarms

  • @Entity
public class UserAlarms
extends java.lang.Object
    class representing the alarms that each Alarmitron user can generate and store under their credentials
    Author:
    The Alarmitron Team

      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      private java.lang.Integer alarmID
      variable for the id of each alarm generated by a user
      private java.lang.String daysOfWeek
      string representing the days of the week that the user wants the alarm to ring a day is represented by the first letter of the word capitalized, weekdays if Mon-Fri is selected, weekends if Sat and Sun are selected, and everyday if every day is selected
      private boolean isEnabled
      whether or not the alarm is active or not
      private java.lang.String label
      optional label for alarm set by user
      private boolean snooze
      boolean for whether or not snooze should be applied to alarm
      private java.lang.String timeOfDay
      string representing the time of the alarm in 24 hour format
      private boolean vibration
      boolean for whether or not alarm should make device vibrate
